OL,3,C'I love you forever,' says mum of
OL,4,Cwoman who died in bungee jump without
OL,5,Crope
OL,7,FThe mother of a 21-year-old woman who
OL,8,Fdied in a rope jumping incident in
OL,9,FBrazil after instructors failed to
OL,10,Fattach her safety equipment has shared
OL,11,Fher "pain and longing" over her death.
OL,13,FMaria Eduarda Rodrigues de Freitas
OL,14,Ffell an estimated 40 metres (130ft)
OL,15,Ffrom Ponte do Esqueleto, an abandoned
OL,16,Fbridge in Limeira, about 92 miles
OL,17,Fnorth of Sao Paulo, when instructors
OL,18,Fallegedly failed to attach her harness.
OL,26,@yD@Ktp
