OL,3,C'I love you forever,' says mum of
OL,4,Cwoman who died in bungee jump without
OL,5,Crope
OL,7,FFootage of the tragedy appears to show
OL,8,Fde Freitas being carried in the air by
OL,9,Fthree men, after she reportedly asked
OL,10,Fto be launched "aeroplane style" for
OL,11,Fthe jump.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FRope could be seen on the ground, and
OL,19,Funattached, behind the instructors as
OL,20,Fthey proceeded to throw de Freitas
OL,21,Ffrom the bridge in the chilling video.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
