PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781693268
OL,3,C'I love you forever,' says mum of
OL,4,Cwoman who died in bungee jump without
OL,5,Crope
OL,7,FValdenia Rodrigues shared a photo of
OL,8,Fher daughter on social media, writing
OL,9,Falongside it: "That damn rope took you
OL,10,Fforever from me.
OL,12,F"My beloved daughter, you left and
OL,13,Fhere there is only pain and longing. I
OL,14,Flove you forever."
OL,16,FBrazilian police investigator Andrea
OL,17,FLevy told journalists that three men
OL,18,Fwere arrested and could face
OL,19,Fmanslaughter charges over de Freitas'
OL,20,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
