PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781693268
OL,3,C'I love you forever,' says mum of
OL,4,Cwoman who died in bungee jump without
OL,5,Crope
OL,7,F"They do not remember whether they
OL,8,Fforgot to attach (the ropes), or who
OL,9,Fwas supposed to do it, or who failed
OL,10,Fto check. But the fact is, the ropes
OL,11,Fwere not attached to her," Levy said.
OL,13,FThe men were detained following a
OL,14,Fcustody hearing, where the judge
OL,15,Fclassified their conduct as gross
OL,16,Fnegligence, according to Brazilian
OL,17,Fmedia.
OL,26,@sD@ZO]
