OL,3,C'I love you forever,' says mum of
OL,4,Cwoman who died in bungee jump without
OL,5,Crope
OL,7,FA camera worn by de Freitas during her
OL,8,Ffall has also not been found by
OL,9,Fpolice, with suggestions it was taken
OL,10,Ffrom the scene.
OL,12,FThe men said de Freitas' death was an
OL,13,Faccident, it was reported.
OL,15,FDe Freitas was buried on Sunday
OL,16,Fmorning in Jandira, Greater Sao Paulo,
OL,17,Fwhere she lived with her family.
