OL,3,C'I love you forever,' says mum of
OL,4,Cwoman who died in bungee jump without
OL,5,Crope
OL,7,FA nurse who tried to help de Freitas
OL,8,Fafter the incident told Brazilian news
OL,9,Fprogramme Domingo Espetacular that she
OL,10,Fhad initially survived the fall, but
OL,11,Fwas hard to access in the rural area
OL,12,Funder the bridge.
OL,14,FRayza Dias attempted to give her life-
OL,15,Fsaving care, but said she had a weak
OL,16,Fpulse and was breathing heavily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
